        </div>
        <div class="col-md-auto" style="width:25rem">
          <div class="card text-center">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">1900's</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Transport yourself to the dynamic 1900s, where the Medicine Hat General Hospital
                marked a historic milestone as the first regular hospital in "the territories," transforming healthcare
                accessibility. Simultaneously, in Saskatoon, Sisters Guay and Phaneuf led pioneering efforts at St.
                Paul's Hospital, forging new paths and leaving an indelible mark on medical care and innovation in
                Saskatchewan.</p>
              <a href="/timeline/1900" class="btn btn-primary">View</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {{!-- 1910 --}}
      <div class="row justify-content-md-center mt-3">
        <div class="col-md-auto" style="width:25rem">
          <div class="card text-center">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">1910's</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Step into the pivotal year of 1910, where Alberta nurses bravely ventured into the
                "Great War," displaying unwavering dedication. Amidst the chaos, the specter of the Spanish influenza
                cast a heavy shadow, showcasing the resilience and commitment of healthcare heroes in challenging times.
              </p>
              <a href="/timeline/1910" class="btn btn-primary">View</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-auto">
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-auto" style="width:25rem">
        </div>
      </div>

      {{!-- 1920 --}}
      <div class="row justify-content-md-center mt-3">
        <div class="col-md-auto" style="width:25rem">

        </div>
