            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">1920's</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Step back into the vibrant 1920s, a time marked by bold changes and cultural shifts.
                Meet Kate Brightly, a trailblazing figure who captured attention with her daring "bob" hairstyle,
                symbolizing the spirit of independence and liberation that defined the era.</p>
              <a href="/timeline/1920" class="btn btn-primary">View</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

