            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">1940's</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Step into the dynamic 1940s, where healthcare milestones and remarkable individuals
                shape the era. Agnes MacLeod leads wartime healthcare efforts as a courageous nurse. Air ambulance
                services debut, transforming emergency response. Meanwhile, Georgiana Chartier's work at the Saskatoon
                Sanatorium highlights the fight against tuberculosis, demonstrating healthcare resilience in combating
                infectious diseases.</p>
              <a href="/timeline/1940" class="btn btn-primary">View</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {{!-- 1950 --}}
      <div class="row justify-content-md-center mt-3">
        <div class="col-md-auto" style="width:25rem">
          <div class="card text-center">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">1950's</h5>
              <p class="card-text">In the 1950s, nurses played a vital role in fighting polio and caring for affected
                communities. Training courses for nursing housekeepers emphasized clean healthcare environments, while
                psychiatric nursing gained recognition, reflecting a growing understanding of mental health needs.</p>
              <a href="/timeline/1950" class="btn btn-primary">View</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-auto">
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-auto" style="width:25rem">
        </div>
      </div>

